x=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mcg1665702702535.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mcg1665702702535.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mcg1665702702535.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mcg1665702702535\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\"> Database Behavior\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the entity is stored in a database. If <code class=\"ph codeph\">N</code>, the\n         <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Data Access</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Database Path</span> property values\n      are ignored. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mcg1665702702535__section_w1658ab1b5b1_w1659ab1b5_w1660ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mcg1665702702535__table_d11120e1_d11121e1_d11122e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mcg1665702702535__table_d11120e1_d11121e1_d11122e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mcg1665702702535__table_d11120e1_d11121e1_d11122e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mcg1665702702535__table_d11120e1_d11121e1_d11122e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">\"\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mcg1665702702535__table_d11120e1_d11121e1_d11122e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value inherited from the Supertype Entity.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mcg1665702702535__table_d11120e1_d11121e1_d11122e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Y</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mcg1665702702535__table_d11120e1_d11121e1_d11122e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Entity data is stored in database.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mcg1665702702535__table_d11120e1_d11121e1_d11122e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">N</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mcg1665702702535__table_d11120e1_d11121e1_d11122e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Entity data is not stored in a database.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mcg1665702702535__section_e55_gmb_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d838430e148\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mcg1665702702535__p_d98033e1_d98034e1_d98035e1\">The value of this property can only be set for Modeled\n            Entity. It cannot be changed in a Subtype Entity or Component Entity.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mcg1665702702535__section_vbs_hmb_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d838430e157\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mcg1665702702535__ul_cxd_jmb_pwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mcg1665702702535__li_d39704e1_d39705e1_d39706e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uqv1665702561461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uqv1665702561461.html\" title=\"An Entity is an abstract data type that defines a logical data aggregation and its associated default characteristics and behavior. It may be mapped to a table in a DBMS, and is most frequently used to represent the application data, but it can also represent transient data, a collection of controls, or constant data.\">Entity</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jlp1665702702609.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Data Access</a><p>Defines how an entity will access the data store—via a database path, or via an entity service.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyp1665702702678.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Database Path</a><p>DBMS path to use when storing occurrences of this entity. This is a named route to the Uniface DBMS connector used to connect to the database. Valid values are Uniface default paths ($DEF, $SYS, $UUU), supported databases and file formats, and user-defined paths. The default is DEF.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Database Behavior Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Database Behavior Determines whether the entity is stored in a database. If N , the Data Access and Database Path property values are ignored. Value Description \"\" Value inherited from the Supertype Entity. Y Entity data is stored in database. N Entity data is not stored in a database. Description The value of this property can only be set for Modeled Entity. It cannot be changed in a Subtype Entity or Component Entity. Applies To Entity Related Links Data Access Defines how an entity will access the data store—via a database path, or via an entity service. Database Path DBMS path to use when storing occurrences of this entity. This is a named route to the Uniface DBMS connector used to connect to the database. Valid values are Uniface default paths ($DEF, $SYS, $UUU), supported databases and file formats, and user-defined paths. The default is DEF. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}